Variability of species in the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hull" authorityYear="1944" box="[553,848,507,536]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Merodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="34" pageNumber="122" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bombiformis">Merodon bombiformis</taxonomicName>
